name: -SUKAIRAIN-
description:
I was always drawn to cars as a kid, and something about these metal boxes still does.
The passion for automobiles continues to grow, and i doubut it will ever stop. It started with exotic imports, then moved on to american muscle and finally settled on the japanese domestic market.
It's my dream to one day own a R34 GTR!

This piece is dedicated to the everlasting love of cars!

resolution- 5400x6750
